---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="必去景点 - 盐色运城" description="运城必去景点指南：七彩盐湖、解州关帝庙、永乐宫、鹳雀楼、普救寺、后土祠等经典目的地。">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">必去景点</h1>
      <p class="text-stone max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">运城最值得打卡的自然与人文景观，从七彩盐湖到千年古建</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <article class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-salt-pink/30 to-pool/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">盐湖风光</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">七彩盐湖</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">世界三大硫酸钠型内陆盐湖之一，因矿物质浓度和温度变化呈现出红、粉、绿、琥珀等七彩斑斓的湖面，被称为"中国死海"。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">最佳：夏秋季</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">建议游览：半天</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-brick/20 to-amber/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">关帝庙建筑</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">解州关帝庙</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">全国最大的关帝庙，始建于隋开皇九年，被誉为"关庙之祖"。建筑群沿中轴线层层递进，气势恢宏。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">国保单位</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">建议游览：2小时</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-amber/20 to-salt-dark/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">永乐宫壁画</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">永乐宫</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">元代道教建筑群，以《朝元图》壁画闻名于世，是中国古代壁画的巅峰之作，总面积达960平方米。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">国保单位</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">建议游览：2小时</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-pool/20 to-amber/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">鹳雀楼远眺</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">鹳雀楼</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">中国四大名楼之一，王之涣"白日依山尽，黄河入海流"即诞生于此。登楼远眺，黄河蜿蜒尽收眼底。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">4A景区</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">建议游览：1.5小时</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-salt-pink/20 to-brick/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">普救寺古塔</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">普救寺</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">《西厢记》故事发生地，寺内莺莺塔以奇特的回音效应闻名——以石击塔，回音如蛙鸣。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">国保单位</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">建议游览：2小时</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-amber/20 to-salt-dark/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">后土祠祭祀</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">后土祠</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">古代皇帝祭祀地神的重要场所，汉武帝曾多次亲临。秋风楼是其标志性建筑，古朴典雅。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">国保单位</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-salt-dark/10 rounded">建议游览：2小时</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
